|last = Clinkard
|first = C. E. 
|title = The Uses of Juices
|accessdate = 2013-05-17
|date = 1993-05-01
|isbn =9780787301781
|pages = 24
|quote =In fact strawberry juice is one of the best skin-cleansing juices known. It is mildly laxative and acts on the kidneys.
}}</ref>而且，草莓含有[[維生素C|維生素C]]<ref>{{cite book
|coauthors = Philip C. Calder, Catherine J. Field
|title = Nutrition and immune function [electronic resource<nowiki>]</nowiki>
|accessdate = 2013-05-17
|isbn =9780851998763
}}</ref>，而維生素C可維持免疫系統<ref>{{cite book
